{"tid":295964,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"棚牙真係好撚重要","createTime":"2017-06-24T07:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T09:04:11.000Z","uid":54344,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"182c7740c72541e5cc304d21dac7b393e1768942","tid":295964,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T07:46:00.000Z","msg":"前排發生左啲意外撞斷左一對門牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n兩三日前杜牙根，遲啲又要去搞牙套之類嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 計埋都幾皮野，簡直係比人㩒鳩住拎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做手術時又痛(一劑麻醉唔撚得，結果一下鑽落黎，最後打多左三劑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，食野宜家又唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係健康無價，各位巴絲刷乾淨啲牙，小心啲，希望大家身體健康啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577f44f52e4048c7f93e6bfde3f713453c06e269","tid":295964,"uid":97708,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T07:57:49.000Z","msg":"真 自己刷牙刷得衰<br />\n上年洗牙痛到仆街<br />\n係張洗牙床到抽搐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4bc28714684f32bcc19247a7b3abdf767ccaf54","tid":295964,"uid":33022,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T08:00:14.000Z","msg":"早掛種返兩隻牙，朋友介紹打左折都要$42000<br />\n貴撚到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4aaf6312e73edbc31de6256fcf56a62027d9431","tid":295964,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T08:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"