":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:56:52.000Z","msg":"睇字都覺得痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老人家成日話牙痛慘過大病<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c394d36808f9e1eeb8027cdd44e01da3531f3d9b","tid":295964,"uid":104088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:58:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4bad20ae08b11787f77d2b6e819b6dace45028a","tid":295964,"uid":79373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:00:38.000Z","msg":"淨係剝哂牙肉四隻智慧齒洗咗近四皮<br />\n勝在手勢好"},{"pid":"3b11f2b0883420e68d18ec8cb777be73aeda6d20","tid":295964,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:13:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錢都唔係問題 <br />\n問題係一世隻牙都唔會好返 以後要就住就住食野 先慘</blockquote><br />\n係啊，四十年後又係等仆街。。。"},{"pid":"0f6b0fbd8aeac9f6beca254639f85d49602de687","tid":295964,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:14:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>保重呀南仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吉妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6419144b1f3638765a5eb92e28e2d17d421dcc","tid":295964,"uid":124146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:28:41.000Z","msg":"我哥都係咁，完全明白！洗好多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33fbeee8fe4f0b0eb01b5a19ebb73ebd04267fc","tid":295964,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:30:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我哥都係咁，完全明白！洗好多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n洗老豆老母錢先心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25bcf399df171c24fa4f9a38007b36309f49f11d","tid":295964,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:32:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真 自己刷牙刷得衰<br />\n上年洗牙痛到仆街<br />\n係張洗牙床到抽搐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n射精咩抽搐"},{"pid":"dbf10915b9b8b8980bfbcb8df56918971153a702","tid":295964,"uid":124146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:36:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我哥都係咁，完全明白！洗好多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n洗老豆老母錢先心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n十幾年前返大陸整左幾千蚊，前排門牙位生瘡，係香港搵牙醫搞洗左萬幾蚊，睇見都肉赤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要好好保養，咬野又要就力，睇見都覺得辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd1e80e1dac46e02f30b90592c26deb41b1a852a","tid":295964,"uid":105445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:39:47.000Z","msg":"想cool牙 但係醫生話要剝曬4隻智慧齒先 其實兩隻打橫生 要打碎佢地 攪到唔敢做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b8a31a62412bf49a012c558ddea17668ea34cf9","tid":295964,"uid":54344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:45:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想cool牙 但係醫生話要剝曬4隻智慧齒先 其實兩隻打橫生 要打碎佢地 攪到唔敢做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打橫生就一定要剝架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e26a546ec8bd944ac7421032ae6d6600947e2f0","tid":295964,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T18:39:48.000Z","msg":"嘩屌成四皮嘢，即刻去刷牙"},{"pid":"0d6e9b2cbc80737158e396b8645676907c31dbae","tid":295964,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T18:40:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前排發生左啲意外撞斷左一對門牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n兩三日前杜牙根，遲啲又要去搞牙套之類嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 計埋都幾皮野，簡直係比人㩒鳩住拎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做手術時又痛(一劑麻醉唔撚得，結果一下鑽落黎，最後打多左三劑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，食野宜家又唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係健康無價，各位巴絲刷乾淨啲牙，小心啲，希望大家身體健康啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都杜左三隻<br />\n以後唔敢亂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be145a34d488a0758ea6fa7b07a835ce8989f49","tid":295964,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T18:44:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘩屌成四皮嘢，即刻去刷牙</blockquote><br />\n牙唔痛，荷包都痛啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5ee063738e71408eca91d6c5187fd415344daf","tid":295964,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:33:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想cool牙 但係醫生話要剝曬4隻智慧齒先 其實兩隻打橫生 要打碎佢地 攪到唔敢做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打橫生就一定要剝架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔一定<br />\n我4隻生哂,得1隻橫生<br />\n但冇理咁耐都冇病冇痛<br />\n反而正常生果邊發過炎<br />\n消完炎之後醫生建議我剥正常生果邊既上下智慧齒,要5千幾蚊<br />\n窮撚又係冇理到,到而家都係冇病冇痛<br />\n但KEEP住1年洗1次牙同埋日日刷牙刷入D咁樣<br />\n<br />\n不過可能已經蛀撚左<br />\n如果有一日痛我會去睇下牙醫"},{"pid":"bea18568a2acbc6b3fa6ef24d5f097de21e6374b","tid":295964,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:45:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想cool牙 但係醫生話要剝曬4隻智慧齒先 其實兩隻打橫生 要打碎佢地 攪到唔敢做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打橫生就一定要剝架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔一定<br />\n我4隻生哂,得1隻橫生<br />\n但冇理咁耐都冇病冇痛<br />\n反而正常生果邊發過炎<br />\n消完炎之後醫生建議我剥正常生果邊既上下智慧齒,要5千幾蚊<br />\n窮撚又係冇理到,到而家都係冇病冇痛<br />\n但KEEP住1年洗1次牙同埋日日刷牙刷入D咁樣<br />\n<br />\n不過可能已經蛀撚左<br />\n如果有一日痛我會去睇下牙醫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇痛咪好囉，一有事就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394675a7a8bf5ab2b12d5c48e5b3349dc68a610e","tid":295964,"uid":101557,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:45:18.000Z","msg":"箍完牙之後真係好錫住啲牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔敢唔刷"},{"pid":"124bc42a077114d737197349d8f7b150e1b2d5b2","tid":295964,"uid":101557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:46:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想cool牙 但係醫生話要剝曬4隻智慧齒先 其實兩隻打橫生 要打碎佢地 攪到唔敢做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打橫生就一定要剝架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔一定<br />\n我4隻生哂,得1隻橫生<br />\n但冇理咁耐都冇病冇痛<br />\n反而正常生果邊發過炎<br />\n消完炎之後醫生建議我剥正常生果邊既上下智慧齒,要5千幾蚊<br />\n窮撚又係冇理到,到而家都係冇病冇痛<br />\n但KEEP住1年洗1次牙同埋日日刷牙刷入D咁樣<br />\n<br />\n不過可能已經蛀撚左<br />\n如果有一日痛我會去睇下牙醫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實到會痛係已經好撚嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75d6c8d9a37d60f2a8a7b5100e819261e24d39e","tid":295964,"uid":16713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:48:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有需要就快啲去<br />\n呢個係我成世人最感恩既決定<br />\n唯一後悔就係無早啲箍"},{"pid":"3c4ddac5c6375fa78d630e73ba0e332fc7d5d99c","tid":295964,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:48:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>箍完牙之後真係好錫住啲牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔敢唔刷</blockquote><br />\n遲啲我箍埋，又洗多幾皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc91126f4e498437c9b552e652caff50ef99855c","tid":295964,"uid":48633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:57:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前排發生左啲意外撞斷左一對門牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n兩三日前杜牙根，遲啲又要去搞牙套之類嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 計埋都幾皮野，簡直係比人㩒鳩住拎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做手術時又痛(一劑麻醉唔撚得，結果一下鑽落黎，最後打多左三劑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，食野宜家又唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係健康無價，各位巴絲刷乾淨啲牙，小心啲，希望大家身體健康啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同你一樣，但我係成隻牙飛撚左出黎，牙腳見到曬"},{"pid":"91956d144418267df4351299bd546265b8387053","tid":295964,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T20:07:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>前排發生左啲意外撞斷左一對門牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n兩三日前杜牙根，遲啲又要去搞牙套之類嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 計埋都幾皮野，簡直係比人㩒鳩住拎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做手術時又痛(一劑麻醉唔撚得，結果一下鑽落黎，最後打多左三劑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，食野宜家又唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係健康無價，各位巴絲刷乾淨啲牙，小心啲，希望大家身體健康啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同你一樣，但我係成隻牙飛撚左出黎，牙腳見到曬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係斷到見牙肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c023f954ab4c1cafea71ba107cd2fa8b385a28bc","tid":295964,"uid":102589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T20:13:52.000Z","msg":"冇左門牙係咪好樣衰？ 出街要戴口罩？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  細個炒單車差啲瀨嘢  好在落地落得好 淨係hi崩左少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce2a2352952574ce92e648f0a2d6cada7f14aec","tid":295964,"uid":65598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T20:17:25.000Z","msg":"成日聽人講要種牙，點樣先要種?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733382e82d4ac21f0a9328fb968a7401402591f3","tid":295964,"uid":11909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T20:22:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早掛種返兩隻牙，朋友介紹打左折都要$42000<br />\n貴撚到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n種韓國牌子$36000咋喎<br />\n你種瑞士牌子？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8964b83a289042f6e1a7d745d08ee0cc61451c05","tid":295964,"uid":11909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T20:24:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日聽人講要種牙，點樣先要種?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇左牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔想用假牙/牙橋<br />\n因為牙骨冇左牙會萎縮<br />\n假牙冇真牙咁好力<br />\n牙橋會令左右兩隻牙受損"},{"pid":"eae3d0af8048282bc811cb3d00a620d1ae82b7e3","tid":295964,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T20:27:40.000Z","msg":"睇牙真係好貴<br />\n想知外國係咪都係咁"},{"pid":"dfc8b13c75783f7bb80cfde5f8db992c5954bb39","tid":295964,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T20:29:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有需要就快啲去<br />\n呢個係我成世人最感恩既決定<br />\n唯一後悔就係無早啲箍</blockquote><br />\n點解， 因為靚？"},{"pid":"ede104cdc7ca3daf58ffd25d3aca3643d387a412","tid":295964,"uid":40,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T20:31:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇牙真係好貴<br />\n想知外國係咪都係咁</blockquote><br />\n外國聽識仲貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbb6e8d9037a456070a93b2f781dbab843943082","tid":295964,"uid":40,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T20:31:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇牙真係好貴<br />\n想知外國係咪都係咁</blockquote><br />\n外國聽講仲貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"61dca6c296829e8195fa03550b455091c3aa99d1","tid":295964,"uid":55810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T20:35:34.000Z","msg":"下排兩隻智慧齒打橫生 次次食完野都攝住晒 出街都要帶埋包牙籤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cdf64e42e6dba8762511e2f94629f0025b108b6","tid":295964,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T20:36:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成日聽人講要種牙，點樣先要種?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇左牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔想用假牙/牙橋<br />\n因為牙骨冇左牙會萎縮<br />\n假牙冇真牙咁好力<br />\n牙橋會令左右兩隻牙受損</blockquote><br />\n咁種牙係咪好怪， 牙肉萎縮咗即使你種咗隻牙都冇牙肉包住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38d2c92f86d0338d605f5eee0ec197288fdde5e","tid":295964,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T20:40:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下排兩隻智慧齒打橫生 次次食完野都攝住晒 出街都要帶埋包牙籤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同我一樣， 不過我得一隻， 好啲<br />\n有時牙籤撩唔到要用牙縫刷"},{"pid":"3c479db677982bf9e176b703b5d942e51e3d43cd","tid":295964,"uid":11909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T20:42:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成日聽人講要種牙，點樣先要種?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇左牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔想用假牙/牙橋<br />\n因為牙骨冇左牙會萎縮<br />\n假牙冇真牙咁好力<br />\n牙橋會令左右兩隻牙受損</blockquote><br />\n咁種牙係咪好怪， 牙肉萎縮咗即使你種咗隻牙都冇牙肉包住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n種左落去就唔會再萎縮 好神奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16e8a29280ea29fff1edba5846fd8afa56dca9ba","tid":295964,"uid":75226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T20:42:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有需要就快啲去<br />\n呢個係我成世人最感恩既決定<br />\n唯一後悔就係無早啲箍</blockquote><br />\n點解， 因為靚？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n箍牙真係唔會後悔，只會後悔太遲箍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a24178ca0064c24eb418a3561435ca4916233a","tid":295964,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T21:34:11.000Z","msg":"銀包同牙都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"308176b6071590e08f0f5a5664b90b2951539a5c","tid":295964,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T21:57:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成日聽人講要種牙，點樣先要種?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇左牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔想用假牙/牙橋<br />\n因為牙骨冇左牙會萎縮<br />\n假牙冇真牙咁好力<br />\n牙橋會令左右兩隻牙受損</blockquote><br />\n咁種牙係咪好怪， 牙肉萎縮咗即使你種咗隻牙都冇牙肉包住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n種左落去就唔會再萎縮 好神奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/25/055526_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F25%2F055526_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ccf0a7cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即係好似呢幅圖咁， 左圖種嗰位牙肉係平嘅， 種完之後就好似右圖咁牙肉自己生番上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c077d49a6cbf74b0676cdda02b3404649156bcdb","tid":295964,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T21:59:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有需要就快啲去<br />\n呢個係我成世人最感恩既決定<br />\n唯一後悔就係無早啲箍</blockquote><br />\n點解， 因為靚？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n箍牙真係唔會後悔，只會後悔太遲箍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都有幾隻唔齊心思思想箍"},{"pid":"f6fc561583e15c225d4510d813fa5389d7da287c","tid":295964,"uid":120581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T22:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b6f32531cbee5601031835c557f551597ac1ab","tid":295964,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T23:07:38.000Z","msg":"台灣睇牙一律100台紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea24a0664ed81542d0023afc547e0c33ae18511","tid":295964,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T01:22:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇牙真係好貴<br />\n想知外國係咪都係咁</blockquote><br />\n外國聽講仲貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n至少我加拿大同之前住荷蘭都係法定價錢，例如杜牙根呢一個手術都定好幾錢，牙套又幾錢，一張X-ray幾錢。全部有曬價目，全部牙醫都要跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66f3ea39caa7603fe1c6fd71f8dd8f8a73a6e611","tid":295964,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T01:24:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台灣睇牙一律100台紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n健保唔同玩法啦，普通睇牙洗牙咪淨係比掛號費囉，大單啲咪又係自費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e3448aeeef84db99957d96089fa8f7ccabf0da","tid":295964,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T01:33:48.000Z","msg":"種牙+cool牙 前前後後駛左7萬幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntotal要用4年幾<br />\n心諗如果跟緊我既牙醫不幸死左 會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0407fb37375ccbe0f5f997a5e8ed0a3a8496f73","tid":295964,"uid":52671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T01:36:11.000Z","msg":"而家杜隻牙根成$7000, <br />\n貴, 可以成日&quot;蚊&quot;左佢, $900<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5270984cb9c033d116ee372342562c58291fbad3","tid":295964,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T01:42:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家杜隻牙根成$7000, <br />\n貴, 可以成日&quot;蚊&quot;左佢, $900<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係差唔多四千左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe388a09d7a7cfe8e5896a4e2f4fb6111569d4a1","tid":295964,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T01:48:28.000Z","msg":"睇完呢個post  <br />\n即刻注重番"},{"pid":"9115b5a2b52221d7b6adcba1f5d4da1706d7c64c","tid":295964,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T02:08:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>種牙+cool牙 前前後後駛左7萬幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntotal要用4年幾<br />\n心諗如果跟緊我既牙醫不幸死左 會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n種牙要時間嘅咩， 我以為淨係箍牙先要"},{"pid":"2bcfa7e8fb6ff7735d3822faf80c8cc89f756c84","tid":295964,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T02:52:23.000Z","msg":"買水牙線保平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38fef2482b561ab790091a1c57796a48c419e8a7","tid":295964,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:09:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買水牙線保平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仆街又係你個打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4894c69aed0ecd7ab4a9800c6919a390dc7da06d","tid":295964,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:10:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>種牙+cool牙 前前後後駛左7萬幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntotal要用4年幾<br />\n心諗如果跟緊我既牙醫不幸死左 會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n種牙要時間嘅咩， 我以為淨係箍牙先要</blockquote><br />\n我諗佢箍牙要姐"},{"pid":"11b4a8e53244d9bdebd27e0421c6bac427bb1b98","tid":295964,"uid":48633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T04:52:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>前排發生左啲意外撞斷左一對門牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n兩三日前杜牙根，遲啲又要去搞牙套之類嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 計埋都幾皮野，簡直係比人㩒鳩住拎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做手術時又痛(一劑麻醉唔撚得，結果一下鑽落黎，最後打多左三劑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，食野宜家又唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係健康無價，各位巴絲刷乾淨啲牙，小心啲，希望大家身體健康啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同你一樣，但我係成隻牙飛撚左出黎，牙腳見到曬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係斷到見牙肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放番上去&gt;等佢實番&gt;社牙根&gt;牙套<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e2bd9ebb9b523b916466fb342c14a924e76bb2","tid":295964,"uid":11909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:41:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成日聽人講要種牙，點樣先要種?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇左牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔想用假牙/牙橋<br />\n因為牙骨冇左牙會萎縮<br />\n假牙冇真牙咁好力<br />\n牙橋會令左右兩隻牙受損</blockquote><br />\n咁種牙係咪好怪， 牙肉萎縮咗即使你種咗隻牙都冇牙肉包住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n種左落去就唔會再萎縮 好神奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/25/055526_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F25%2F055526_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ccf0a7cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即係好似呢幅圖咁， 左圖種嗰位牙肉係平嘅， 種完之後就好似右圖咁牙肉自己生番上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n縮左唔會自己生上去 種左只會令佢停止縮落去<br />\n所以啲牙齒會話冇左隻牙(智慧齒除外)三個月後就好種<br />\n(剝牙之後三個月牙骨牙肉會收縮好 點都會縮少少)<br />\n(如果可以做到杜牙根+牙套 佢地一般都會做杜牙根多過叫你剝再種)"},{"pid":"b6f3ff096e904cb6e771edc0931ff6c298e87811","tid":295964,"uid":11909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:43:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>種牙+cool牙 前前後後駛左7萬幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntotal要用4年幾<br />\n心諗如果跟緊我既牙醫不幸死左 會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n種牙要時間嘅咩， 我以為淨係箍牙先要</blockquote><br />\n冇左隻牙要等三個月先種得 落得種體又要等至少三個月 生返實<br />\n如果加左骨粉再等多兩至四個月不等 <br />\n再印模等兩星期先上實假牙冠<br />\n<br />\n你計下要幾長時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46b690ebc1e711c572c1576824394d52ffa20ad","tid":295964,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:26:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>前排發生左啲意外撞斷左一對門牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n兩三日前杜牙根，遲啲又要去搞牙套之類嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 計埋都幾皮野，簡直係比人㩒鳩住拎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做手術時又痛(一劑麻醉唔撚得，結果一下鑽落黎，最後打多左三劑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，食野宜家又唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係健康無價，各位巴絲刷乾淨啲牙，小心啲，希望大家身體健康啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同你一樣，但我係成隻牙飛撚左出黎，牙腳見到曬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係斷到見牙肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放番上去&gt;等佢實番&gt;社牙根&gt;牙套<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我直頭揾唔返對門牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d79d5be5f0a73e03d307a68cc51b32a3d81b0e7","tid":295964,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T08:51:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>種牙+cool牙 前前後後駛左7萬幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntotal要用4年幾<br />\n心諗如果跟緊我既牙醫不幸死左 會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n種牙要時間嘅咩， 我以為淨係箍牙先要</blockquote><br />\n冇左隻牙要等三個月先種得 落得種體又要等至少三個月 生返實<br />\n如果加左骨粉再等多兩至四個月不等 <br />\n再印模等兩星期先上實假牙冠<br />\n<br />\n你計下要幾長時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁啲人一次種幾隻點食嘢<br />\n舉例撞車令一邊面冇咗幾隻牙， 咁咪有排冇牙食嘢， 而且以我所知甩咗牙嗰位會影響埋附近生長， 例如上層冇咗牙後下層啲牙會自己伸長上去， 咁咪有排煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c26d2e8d138559920d1542d9be939dd076017ed","tid":295964,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T08:53:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成日聽人講要種牙，點樣先要種?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇左牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔想用假牙/牙橋<br />\n因為牙骨冇左牙會萎縮<br />\n假牙冇真牙咁好力<br />\n牙橋會令左右兩隻牙受損</blockquote><br />\n咁種牙係咪好怪， 牙肉萎縮咗即使你種咗隻牙都冇牙肉包住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n種左落去就唔會再萎縮 好神奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/25/055526_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F25%2F055526_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ccf0a7cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即係好似呢幅圖咁， 左圖種嗰位牙肉係平嘅， 種完之後就好似右圖咁牙肉自己生番上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n縮左唔會自己生上去 種左只會令佢停止縮落去<br />\n所以啲牙齒會話冇左隻牙(智慧齒除外)三個月後就好種<br />\n(剝牙之後三個月牙骨牙肉會收縮好 點都會縮少少)<br />\n(如果可以做到杜牙根+牙套 佢地一般都會做杜牙根多過叫你剝再種)</blockquote><br />\n你做呢行㗎， 定有經驗<br />\n咁清楚嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ac579d4b0b23661ab736a6b2864b2b0af542f7","tid":295964,"uid":5749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T08:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e4edcfac970e95e6d73c136545127a615f2dae3","tid":295964,"uid":3555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T12:34:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d357be7cac7ac413edf7ebc38d4666b2deaa70ef","tid":295964,"uid":11909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:37:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>種牙+cool牙 前前後後駛左7萬幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntotal要用4年幾<br />\n心諗如果跟緊我既牙醫不幸死左 會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n種牙要時間嘅咩， 我以為淨係箍牙先要</blockquote><br />\n冇左隻牙要等三個月先種得 落得種體又要等至少三個月 生返實<br />\n如果加左骨粉再等多兩至四個月不等 <br />\n再印模等兩星期先上實假牙冠<br />\n<br />\n你計下要幾長時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁啲人一次種幾隻點食嘢<br />\n舉例撞車令一邊面冇咗幾隻牙， 咁咪有排冇牙食嘢， 而且以我所知甩咗牙嗰位會影響埋附近生長， 例如上層冇咗牙後下層啲牙會自己伸長上去， 咁咪有排煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以用臨時假牙 ar住啲位先<br />\n同埋只有上面生落去 下面唔會生上去 同埋生得落去唔會係幾個月既事<br />\n例如左邊冇左 仲有右邊 又唔係成排冇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f86b8306382ced3af3aea638138dcc57650d9f59","tid":295964,"uid":11909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:38:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成日聽人講要種牙，點樣先要種?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇左牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔想用假牙/牙橋<br />\n因為牙骨冇左牙會萎縮<br />\n假牙冇真牙咁好力<br />\n牙橋會令左右兩隻牙受損</blockquote><br />\n咁種牙係咪好怪， 牙肉萎縮咗即使你種咗隻牙都冇牙肉包住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n種左落去就唔會再萎縮 好神奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/25/055526_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F25%2F055526_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ccf0a7cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即係好似呢幅圖咁， 左圖種嗰位牙肉係平嘅， 種完之後就好似右圖咁牙肉自己生番上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n縮左唔會自己生上去 種左只會令佢停止縮落去<br />\n所以啲牙齒會話冇左隻牙(智慧齒除外)三個月後就好種<br />\n(剝牙之後三個月牙骨牙肉會收縮好 點都會縮少少)<br />\n(如果可以做到杜牙根+牙套 佢地一般都會做杜牙根多過叫你剝再種)</blockquote><br />\n你做呢行㗎， 定有經驗<br />\n咁清楚嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed1c719f3f32f08afae0bd6fd8ca3ff7b702168","tid":295964,"uid":52671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:30:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n工聯會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}